# LogSurgeScanner - Log Pattern Analyzer

LogSurgeScanner reveals error storms, repeating log lines, and keyword-based spikes in system and app logs.

## Features
- Burst + repetition detection  
- Keyword filtering  
- Timestamp grouping  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/26_LogSurgeScanner.git
cd 26_LogSurgeScanner
python analyze.py
